    S --> OUT[/Structured, spoiler-safe output<br/>summary · watch_for[] · book_vs_show[] · sources[]/]:::out
    OUT --> APP

    GR{{guardrails.py<br/>spoiler callback +<br/>input-safety}}:::guard
    GR -.enforces.- PIPE

